protected abstract static class TagBasedConverter.TagBasedConverterImpl<T> extends Object
Abstract base class for the tag-based converter implementation classes.

    • appendOpeningTagsForAttributes

      protected void appendOpeningTagsForAttributes(List<TagBasedConverter.AttributeChange> attributesToClose)
      Appends opening tags corresponding to the provided attributes. Each attribute in the list represents a specific property-value pair, and this method generates and appends the appropriate tag representations for these attributes in an underlying format.
      Parameters:
      attributesToClose - the list of TagBasedConverter.AttributeChange objects representing the attributes for which opening tags need to be appended

    • appendClosingTagsForAttributes

      protected void appendClosingTagsForAttributes(List<TagBasedConverter.AttributeChange> attributesToClose)
      Appends the appropriate closing tags for the given list of attributes. This method ensures that the closing tags corresponding to the specified attributes are properly added to maintain formatting consistency.
      Parameters:
      attributesToClose - the list of TagBasedConverter.AttributeChange representing attributes for which closing tags should be appended

    • appendOpeningTagsForStyles

      protected abstract void appendOpeningTagsForStyles(List<Style> openingStyles)
      Appends opening tags corresponding to the provided styles. The implementation of this method should generate and append the appropriate tag representations based on the given list of styles.
      Parameters:
      openingStyles - the list of styles for which opening tags should be appended

    • appendClosingTagsForStyles

      protected abstract void appendClosingTagsForStyles(List<Style> closingStyles)
      Appends the required closing tags corresponding to the given list of styles. This method ensures that the associated tags for the specified styles are properly closed, maintaining the integrity of the output format.
      Parameters:
      closingStyles - the list of styles for which the closing tags need to be appended
